column16: Carlos Beltran flies out to left fielder So Taguchi.
Andrew Carpenter intentionally walks Carlos Delgado.
David Wright strikes out swinging, catcher Chris Coste to first baseman Ryan Howard.    Jose Reyes to 3rd.
Luis Castillo out on a sacrifice bunt, third baseman Pedro Feliz to first baseman Ryan Howard.    Jose Reyes to 2nd.
Jose Reyes singles on a soft fly ball to left fielder So Taguchi.
